description: Returns a list of Batch scheduling policies.

parameters.name: nextToken
parameters.description: The nextToken value that's returned from a previous paginated ListSchedulingPolicies request where maxResults was used and the results exceeded the value of that parameter. Pagination continues from the end of the previous results that returned the nextToken value. This value is null when there are no more results to return.

nested_items.name: schedulingPolicies
nested_items.description: A list of scheduling policies that match the request.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the scheduling policy.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The nextToken value to include in a future ListSchedulingPolicies request. When the results of a ListSchedulingPolicies request exceed maxResults, this value can be used to retrieve the next page of results. This value is null when there are no more results to return.
